      In <xref ref="d4-cycles">Problems</xref> and <xref ref="permutation-cycles"/> you found the cycle decomposition of typical elements of the group <m>D_4</m> and of the permutation
      <me>
      \begin{pmatrix}1\amp 2\amp 3\amp 4\amp 5\amp 6\amp 7\amp 8\amp 9\cr
